OL,7,FCar owners in Hampshire say they fear
OL,8,Ffor their family's safety as criminals
OL,9,Fhave been stealing cars in the middle
OL,10,Fof the night.
OL,12,FIt follows a rise in thieves stealing
OL,13,Fhigh-value keyless cars across the
OL,14,FSouth by using electronic devices to
OL,15,Ftrick cars into thinking their key fob
OL,16,Fis close by - allowing it to unlock
OL,17,Fand start the ignition.
OL,19,FKeyless car technology is responsible
OL,20,Ffor a boom in car thefts, according to
OL,21,Fcar insurance firm LV General.
