OL,7,FThe company found that 2023 was the
OL,8,Fworst year on record for thefts.
OL,10,FDuring 2022/23, there were 480 keyless
OL,11,Fcar thefts in Hampshire and the Isle
OL,12,Fof Wight, which is up from 135 thefts
OL,13,Fthe year before.
OL,15,FIt only took brazen thieves 90 seconds
OL,16,Fto steal Sarah Newth's car straight
OL,17,Foff her driveway in Southampton.
